					<![CDATA[
						 <p>The only way I can describe how I feel about this is to say it feels like SCP-1424.</p> <p>Unfortunate circumstances and human desire, powerful combination for an SCP. Theres somethign about it I dont like but i cant put my finger on it. Struggling with the dates if I'm honest, never understood that format. To me it would be like writing the time in minutes, then seconds, then hours lol.</p> <p>Not going to vote on this one. If I come back to it I may work out my gripe.</p> 
