					<![CDATA[
						 <blockquote> <p>Contact with SCP-1651 causes a cognition-affecting anomaly to occur.</p> </blockquote> <p>I don't think you mean cognition, as that refers more to thought patterns and processes. This is more of a sensory affect (as noted in the tags). As far as I can tell from reading this, the subjects are able to think clearly while experiencing the affect, so cognition doesn't really fit.</p> 
				 	]]>
